content.detailedDescription:
When i was 7 years old myself, my sister, mother and father were waiting in our car to enter the highland drive-in theater in salt lake city. we saw a silver (metallic) colored disk shaped craft hovering in the air a few blocks east of us, between us and the mountains.

it made no sound and didn't have any lights, it just hovered (was still) in the air, then it headed north along the face of the mountains at an incredible speed, it was out of site in a second. it then reversed its course (it was out of site when it changed direction) and came back along the same path heading south along the face of the mountains until out of sight.

this was seen at dusk, the sun had just set, but it was still light and we saw it clearly. it looked like the classic flying saucer, metallic, disk shaped, thicker in height in the middle and tapering to the outside edges, with kind of a dome shape in the middle on both the top and bottom, the bottom dome shape smaller than the one on top.

it kept the same altitude the whole time, while hovering and moving (did not go up or down), just hovered went north out of site, then came back from the north and went south until out of site.

other people at the drive-in also saw it, everyone looked but no one said anything or really seemed to react to what they saw (once it was gone no one said anything just continued as if nothing had happened). shock perhaps?

my older sister was at our home on the west side of the valley sitting outside on the porch at that time and also saw it, our home was on a hill with an unobstructed view of the north and east sides of the valley. 

i remember my parents reading a short article in the newspaper a day or two later about people reporting seeing this disk. my family did not report it then.

i can't remember the exact date, but it was summer 1967 a friday or saturday and the full moon about midway in its path across the sky. i looked up full moon time in the summer of 1967 and reported the july 21 date because that is the only date that the full moon would have been in that position in the sky that summer on a friday or saturday.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path with directional change
content.summary: My family and i saw a flying saucer hover and then move at incredible speed while waiting in car to enter a drive-in theater.

content.detailedDescription: My niece and i returned home from shopping and noticed a bright light to the left of our duplex. it looked like a huge star dangling from the sky. it swung back and forth in the sky making incredible angles. my niece was terrified, i asked her to get my camcorder and she ran inside. i continued to watch, the light kept moving then i saw a black triangle shape come toward me . i was on the road at that point, under a streetlight. the triangular shaped craft moved overhead, seemed to barely make it over the telephone poles. there was a vibration or humming sound as it passed very slowly over my head.The underside of the ufo was lit up with hundreds of lights. it looked like a city one would see from an airplane at night. the craft was gigantic, at least 3 football fields long. i could hear the traffic on nearby 395 going by, but other than the hum there was no other sound. i suddenly realized that i was under the street light and exposed to the craft,and also that my niece had not returned. i went inside to fetch the camcorder and when i went back out the huge craft was gone.
content.summary: My niece and i saw a night light to the left of our townhouse. it looked like a huge star. it swung up and down as if  a pendulum.

content.summary: We saw 6 white ufos ascending at a 45 degree angle.

content.detailedDescription:
I was smoking a cigarette out of my window, i see planes flying over regular flightpaths, and one flew over the horizon with what seems like searchlights/bright car headlights, i said to my girlfriend, that looks well strange as it was just above the tree line on the horizon, initially i thought it was a helicopter as we have a few roaming about up here but there was no sound just a low frequency buzz, as it flew toward i noticed planes on a usual flightpath actually performing sudden flight corrections which was odd which continued afterwards, and the next day i hardly saw no planes passing overhead, but as the craft came close it took a sudden dip at the back slowed its course as to hover slightly which is when i noticed the flame like underbelly that jets have and then i started freaking out as i saw no nose cone on the craft, it almost looked like the batwing, had a solid red light on the tip on the right wing and solid green on the left, two huge lights dead centre at a 45 degree angle. i nearly text my friend who is also into ufo's so forth, and he text me the next day saying he had a dream about me and an alien craft that was matt black flying over my house, without describing it to him he told me the distinct colour of matt black.

a week later, 7 orange orbs separated  from one in the distance and were pinging like atoms

and a week after this me and girlfriend again saw the same craft we saw in the first report going straight over us in the opposite direction to which all major flights arrive into to come to manchester airport

my uncle was an air commmodore and a training instructor for years in the air force so i know my planes and jets. and these were not a known craft, i have lived in this address for nearly 30 years and know a plane or something else
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: This was the first up close ncounter witnessed by me and my girlfriend, i know every flight path and distinct plane shape and sound over my house

content.detailedDescription:
It was mid afternoon. i was visiting a friend's daughter's house and we were taking the garbage out. charles was in the garage. i was at the top of the driveway. i looked up and saw a white orb floating along from the ne. before i could call charles, another orb appeared and then another. they were moving in a straight line at the speed of a jet, or maybe slightly slower. they stayed the same distance apart as they moved in a straight line silently across the sky to the sw. they were up as high as jets fly, maybe slightly lower. i thought to myself, 'here we go again, i'm seeing something no one will believe'.

i called charles. he came up and saw them too. we stood and watched until we could see them no more. they disappeared behind the vancouver skyline never changing course. they never emitted a light, although they were white and it was a sunny day, so it would have been hard to tell. they never changed colour or course. they never made a sound or left a trail. they reminded me of the object video taped over the los angeles area in january 2016. 

i had seen an orb before many years ago in the early '80's in my bedroom in ottawa, ontario. it was a blue one slightly bigger than a basketball and the light it emitted cast a blue that was brighter than the object. the object had two blue points of light spinning around inside of it the points of light were bright, but the lights left a dull trail inside the ball as they spun around rapidly. i had been asleep and opened my eyes to notice the white walls of my room were lit up blue. then i looked up about 10 inches to a foot over my chest, there was the orb. at first i was just marvelling at it, then i realized what i was looking at, got freaked out, sat straight up and the sphere disappeared in an instant, my walls return to white, my room dark. freaky, not sure what it was. when i awoke, i was hearing what i call 'holy music' which is a meditation technic i practice. the sound is what i guess the universal vibration might be.
content.summary: Three white orbs approx 30 feet wide no lights noise or trail

content.detailedDescription: I was taking my dogs outside in the backyard around 8pm.  i looked up in the sky to see what appeared to be a small red light.  but you could tell it was further up in the sky (around the same height as commercial airliners fly when they are getting close to the airport).  it moved high in the sky, and was coming in the direction of my house (coming from the west).  it moved slowly, then hovered for a few seconds, and then started to move again.  but i noticed that when it hovered, it seemed to go from a red light to a bluish -green light.  it sort of looked like it was spinning.  then, i noticed a commercial jet come from the east.  there is an airport nearby, and we have lots of air traffic.  the red light was in the direct path of the jet.  and right before it looked as if the two were going to collide, the red light moved out of the way.  the light the moved slowly in a nw direction and started to descend behind the tree line until i could no longer see it.
content.summary: Red light slowly moves over house, and then into path of airplane.

content.detailedDescription:
Being a trained military observer i have had now 2 encounters with lights that are performing impossible flight characteristics of known civilian and military (to include top secret military) aircraft i know of. the first of which my daughter and i witnessed in february of 2006 at about 2200 hrs. a light passing over head at an altitude of 80,000 ft or higher, the light moving at extremely high speed stopped without slowing down, stayed stationary for about 10 seconds, then took off at the same rate of speed from the exact direction it came. both my daughter and i were in shock.

the 2nd encounter happened last month april 2016. i saw a light appear out of no where in the night sky about 2200 hrs, the distance from the light was extreme, the altitude was unknown, the light pulsated white to blue to red, traveled horizontally across the sky at extreme speed, changing direction 180 degrees back and forth for about 2-3 minutes then stopped and shot directly upwards out of sight at even a greater speed.
content.summary: Two encounters with unexplained lights, one with my daughter in 2006, and again april 2016

content.detailedDescription:
1.) i noticed something very strange, and almost scary, when i saw a brightly-colored object. i saw this object when i was stopped at a stop sign in jackson avenue, salisbury mills ny.

2.) i first noticed it is once i stopped at the sign stop, to to make a left, and saw this unnatural and highly strange hovering and moving a straight line about a train trestle that crosses a road and a large field. 

3.) having taken biology, and being an atheist, i tend to observe things in a critical way. it caught me so off guard. i could not take my eyes off of it, because i was so memorized by what i saw, that i didn't even think to bring out my cell phone. it definitely wasn't a plane or helicopter. unless the train station using from strange, pulsating orange o, but i don't know. my mind was racing, trying to figure out what it was

4.) this object was a perfectly round sphere. as i was stopped in my car at the stop sign, i got a clear view of it. it was hovering above a train trestle and moved at a constant speed, until the train track led into schunemuck mountain. it was a bright orange color. it was pulsating as it was slowly moving i didn't hear anything. this was very large as well. 

5.) after the sighting, i called my boyfriend and i was absolutely freaking out, because of course i was by myself! once i got home, i told my family, but it seems like no one believed me. i don't talk about it a lot, because i'm sure people would think that i'm lying, and 

i don't wan't to sound crazy (which it was i am reporting it). i was terrified for the rest of that night, wracking my brain about what it was. i needed an answer, because it's so hard to see something like that and not be able to tell too many people. as i watched this object i wish:1.) someone was with me 2.) videotaped it 3.) waited for another car to drive by me so they could see it too. 

6.) the craft disappeared once after it followed the tracks on the tran trestle. these tracks lead into the side of a mountain. this is where it went. i tried speeding down the road to get another look, but i never say it again.

content.detailedDescription:

forgive my english... its my second lenguage. 

i used a panasonic model no. dmc-ts20 (1:3.9 / 45-18 asph)

content.detailedDescription: So it was about 7 o'clock, i was heading out to cover my tomato plants so that the winter cold won't damage them. that's when the force of habit urged me to observe orion. as i looked away again, towards the direction of my plants. i observed this very bright star in the southern sky, at the time i was walking towards the plants and all stars seemed to be naturally moving with me. but i stopped and looked at the bright light in the south, and saw that it was not one of the stars, but it was actually very gradually moving, it moved without a sound or trail. i've seen this happen around here at least four times. that's when i ran inside to get my sister to show her that i wasn't crazy, that's when she also observed the object. the light moved in an eastern direction, very slowly, and for about 3 minutes we watched it fly and than it just disappeared into the sky like coffee would when you throw it in water, we were completely speechless. we had no idea what it could have been, but since many people around here claim to have been the victim of close encounters with these lights and objects, we figured that it must be a ufo. we were afraid of what was going to happen next. i loaded the rifle and put it next to my bed, after we heard these strange noises coming from outside. a while later there was something on the roof, it might have been a cat, but at the time i was so terrified that the only thing i could think of was being abducted by big headed aliens.
content.summary: Sighting of a strange light near my farm

content.detailedDescription:
My brother, mom and i drove to top of maybee mines to take pics of sunset. mom
had been cooped up in house with broken shoulder so we took her for a drive. i stood on old log and started taking pictures for a panoramic shot about a second apart. when reviewing pictures i saw what appeared as a lense flare and zoomed in. i saw the object, and saw in the next 4 photos. the object followed a path forming a backwards 3 from my aspect, which interestingly in sanskrit means "i exist". the object appeared to change form in the last two pictures from a large structured craft to an orb as it got close to us. as a former field investigator i have ruled out the lense flare possibility because the object was in motion and does not form a direct line between the camera lense and the light source (sun). the pictures have not been modified for contrast or any other enhancement methods. they are in sequential order. zoom in to see plasma field; i believe the dimishing area is a result of deceleration as it entered a lower altitude (note red "aura". i used a samsung galaxy core prevail cellphone camera.
content.summary: Uap descended to close within our vicinity when taking pictures.

content.detailedDescription: I was getting home at 3:35pm on may 18th 2016. i got out of my car and was walking to my door. in my field of vision to my left i saw a black object in the sky above a line of trees behind my house. at first i just assumed it was a bird riding on an air current. then i saw some actual birds and realized the object looked nothing like the birds. i watched the object moving very slowly from east to west. the weather was overcast with solid cloud cover and the object was below the clouds at what i believe to be a relatively low altitude. it was moving much too slow to be an airplane and i don't think it was a helicopter of any kind. i didn't hear any sound that corresponded to the object. in the five minutes the object was visible to me i took three pictures on my phone but the object did not appear in any of them. the object appeared solid black and i couldn't determine its exact shape. when i lost sight of the object i think it had stopped moving from east to west and ascended straight up into the clouds and out of my sight.
content.summary: Unusual object in sky near my house
